{"ts": "2026-06-09T05:53:52.089226+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "I've gathered all the necessary information. Now I understand what needs to be done:\n\n1. **`docs/api/authentication.md`** exists but has only placeholder content - needs proper authentication documentation\n2. **`mkdocs.yml`** needs to add the Authentication page to the API navigation section\n\nLet me implement both changes:", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 904, "prompt_tokens": 10215, "total_tokens": 11119, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 172, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 9792, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0010057362, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0002192562, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00078648}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780984410-gkeli8c1kEe2tUgzAroW", "finish_reason": "tool_calls", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019eaaf1-6e5f-7400-8c9c-52479187c7f2-0", "tool_calls": [{"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T16_R02_C01_A02", "branch": "main", "path": "docs/api/authentication.md", "content": "# Authentication\n\nThis page describes how to authenticate requests against the API.\n\n## Overview\n\nAll API requests must include valid credentials. The service supports two authentication methods:\n\n1. **API Key** – pass the key in the `Authorization` header as `Bearer <key>`.\n2. **OAuth 2.0 Client Credentials** – obtain a short-lived access token from the token endpoint and include it in the `Authorization` header.\n\n## API Key Authentication\n\nInclude the API key in every request:\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY\n```\n\nAPI keys are scoped to a single project and can be rotated from the project settings page.\n\n## OAuth 2.0 Client Credentials\n\nExchange your client ID and client secret for an access token:\n\n```\nPOST /oauth/token\nContent-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\n\ngrant_type=client_credentials&client_id=YOUR_ID&client_secret=YOUR_SECRET\n```\n\nThe response contains an `access_token` that is valid for 3600 seconds. Include it in subsequent requests:\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <access_token>\n```\n\n## Token Expiration & Refresh\n\nWhen an access token expires the API returns a `401 Unauthorized` error (see [Errors](errors.md)). Re-authenticate by requesting a new token using the same client-credentials flow described above.\n\n## Best Practices\n\n- Store credentials securely; never commit them to version control.\n- Rotate API keys regularly.\n- Use the shortest token lifetime that fits your workflow.\n", "sha": "95634affc08f65ee1711adb65833a8c392935aae", "message": "docs(api): add authentication reference page with API key and OAuth 2.0 documentation"}, "id": "call_b275a46596aa44178d4a6f7d", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T16_R02_C01_A02", "branch": "main", "path": "mkdocs.yml", "content": "site_name: Clean MkDocs Benchmark\nsite_description: Documentation benchmark repository\nnav:\n  - Home: index.md\n  - Getting Started: getting-started.md\n  - Configuration: configuration.md\n  - API:\n      - Overview: api/overview.md\n      - Authentication: api/authentication.md\n      - Errors: api/errors.md\ntheme:\n  name: material\nmarkdown_extensions:\n  - admonition\n", "sha": "039e25928047e875e2a9186264e36488a2a9b406", "message": "docs(api): add authentication page to navigation"}, "id": "call_26ad2e0e46c54254a47f8e35", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 10215, "output_tokens": 904, "total_tokens": 11119, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9792}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 172}}}}]}}}
